{
  "texts": [
    "Last layer only TracIn is also referred to as TracIn-Last.",
    "Yeh et al. (2022) evaluate TracIn-Last's effectiveness.",
    "See Sect. 5.1.2 for an extended discussion of last-layer similarity.",
    "Note that this HVP is different than s test ∶= (H (T)) -1 ∇ L(z te;(T)) in Eq.",
    "Hammoudeh & Lowd (2022) also provide renormalized versions of representer point and TracIn which are omitted here."
  ]
